{"tid":2257500,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"消息：特朗普對共和黨保持參議院多數黨地位感悲觀","createTime":"2020-10-25T08:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T11:04:14.000Z","uid":28114,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2c0f48e6ef49d62e98ced0efa3a17a80e7655f54","tid":2257500,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T08:06:36.000Z","msg":"美國大選還有8日舉行，總統特朗普同民主黨總統候選人拜登，馬不停蹄加緊拉票，今次大選將同時改選部份參議院議席，美國傳媒報道，特朗普在一場閉門籌款活動中承認，對參議院選情感到悲觀，指共和黨要保持參議院多數黨地位非常困難，他難以支持一些黨內候選人。<br />\n<br />\n共和黨目前在參議院100個議席中佔53席，以微弱優勢佔多數，其中23席要改選；民主黨45席，則有12席改選。民主黨若要成為多數黨，必須守住本身席位，還要從共和黨手中再奪得3到4個席位。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2363211\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2363211&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PSq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=a7d7bc92\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2363211</a>"},{"pid":"fdebddaf17a57a6000523f97b8334c578dd2678f","tid":2257500,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T08:07:48.000Z","msg":"Trump privately tells donors it would be &lsquo;very tough&rsquo; for GOP to hold Senate<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/trump-senate-republicans-election/2020/10/24/f93f5ed0-15f4-11eb-ba42-ec6a580836ed_story.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fpolitics%2Ftrump-senate-republicans-election%2F2020%2F10%2F24%2Ff93f5ed0-15f4-11eb-ba42-ec6a580836ed_story.html&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PSq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=ad767131\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/trump-senate-republicans-election/2020/10/24/f93f5ed0-15f4-11eb-ba42-ec6a580836ed_story.html</a>"},{"pid":"5d083d33b4a262aaf66a7fd29aa21b5437df0a5c","tid":2257500,"uid":167597,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T08:16:05.000Z","msg":"侵侵又告急<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我登必勝<img src=\"